    "801005": {
        "Desc": "Synthesize the Nameless Taboo Medicine of the Royal Court",
        "Tips": "The synthesis of the Nameless Taboo Medicine of the Royal Court requires both Kalpalata Lotuses and Sumeru Roses.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Over here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A Crafting Bench?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What are you going to use this for?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I'm sure you're wondering why I brought Caribert here, to Sumeru."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Well, it's because he needs a medicine that can only be made here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "One which will help him to recover his clarity of mind."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Recover his clarity of mind?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(When we were in The Chasm, Dain said that the curse could not be undone... Is recovery really possible?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I do not hope to break the curse. I am well aware of my powerlessness against the punishment of the gods."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "But it's said that this medicine is imbued with the power of Sumeru's God of Wisdom, and can awaken the mind from a state of deep stupor... It has been used in the past to treat cases of mania."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I believe that it might just work..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Where did you hear of this?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...I read about it in a book from the Royal Library of Khaenri'ah. It was banned, since this medicine requires the power of The Seven to work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "In my youth, Iâ€”I disliked the life of nobility, and craved excitement. I was leafing through some forbidden texts and happened upon it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You know, there must've been a reason it was banned..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It sounds dangerous..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...What other choice do I have? What exactly would you have me do?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "The gods have already punished us! What does one more sin matter now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Alright, don't get too worked up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I understand. No matter what, you have to try."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Never mind, as long as you understand... Iâ€”I'm sorry, I struggle to take control of my mood sometimes... Perhaps a consequence of having lived too long."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "As it happens, I am in dire need of some help to make this medicine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "My hands don't have the dexterity they once did. I fear that they may be decaying from within... all thanks to this curse of immortality."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Okay, to start with, take this ingredient..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "A mushroom?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I've never seen a mushroom of this kind before..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Also, do you have any of Sumeru's regional specialties on hand? I believe they're called... <color=#00E1FFFF>Kalpalata Lotuses</color> and <color=#00E1FFFF>Sumeru Roses</color>."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
