    "801011": {
        "Desc": "Give Eide the water",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Look at this statue... How can I bow before this thing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "God of Wisdom. Look at me."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I will utter no prayer, nor will I sing your praises."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "You and your kind destroyed my home, wrought unfathomable suffering on my compatriots... Yet here I stand before you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "You cannot mock me more than fate itself already has."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "God of Wisdom, I seek not to disavow myself of the sinful blood that flows through my veins. I wish only to beseech you to have pity upon a young and unfortunate soul."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "My son, Caribert... He was turned into a monster before he had the chance to witness anything beautiful in this world... This is no fate for a child."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "If everything the gods have done was in order to have the impious people of Khaenri'ah bow their heads..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Then... I bow to you now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I have given up all I ever stood for..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "All I ask for is a tiny miracle. For Caribert to see this world once more."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Please, god... I beg of you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(I may not know the whole truth behind the cataclysm, but the people of Khaenri'ah have truly suffered...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Why could Khaenri'ah and The Seven not coexist in peace?)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I have made quite enough of a fool of myself for one day. Let's go."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Things will get better."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...Hm."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
