    "801012": {
        "Desc": "Defeat the attacking monsters",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Caribert?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caribert",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(The hilichurl seems almost lifeless. Its reactions to everything are incredibly weak...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Well, we've prepared the medicine. We might as well try it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "With your help, Eide feeds the newly made medicine to the hilichurl."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Caribert? It's me... It's your father. Caribert?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Anything?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Caribert... Please, say something."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Caribert",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I'm sorry I couldn't be at your side when you were born... and that I failed to reach you and mama in time when you both were suffering..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "But I'm here now. Papa's been by your side all these years. I've never left you. Not once."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Are you still angry with me, Caribert?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I know you're awake now... Do you not want to talk to me?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I'm so sorry, Caribert. Forgive me, please! Say something. Anything!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Please... please..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Eide, stop..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It didn't work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Aah!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Gods above! What more do you want from me!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "You took everything from here, and I still bowed to you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I'd give you my very life if only you cared to take it! But you won't even let me die!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...I knew it. I should never have trusted anything that had to do with the gods. I was just deluding myself..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "The gods of this world have never stood with humanity... Not even for a moment!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Calm down, Eide."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There might be other reasons it didn't work."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Other reasons... What do you mean?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Such as... who knows, perhaps the dosage was too low."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Or maybe it takes a full course of treatment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Huh... you really think so...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You have to exhaust all options..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Unless you are ready to give up on Caribert..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Give up? No, no. Never! ...Yes, you're right. I cannot let myself wallow in despair."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Even if I must stay here with him for... fifty years? A hundred? What difference does it make? I do not lack for time..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That's the spirit."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'll keep helping you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(To have infinite time, yet no hope... can only be called torture.)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Let's go. We'll make another dose."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "The most crucial ingredient in this medicine is the unusual mushroom, which makes things complicated... but not impossible."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Where did you get those mushrooms from, anyway?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I grow them. In that field."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Wait, in a field? Like a crop?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...The details don't matter, right? Curb your curiosity and just do as I instruct â€” if you truly wish to help me, that is how you can do it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Fine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "There is a waterfall near the statue I prayed at. I need you to collect some water from there around two in the afternoon."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I'll be here watching Caribert. Once you're back, I will make some fertilizer for the mushrooms."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Got it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Good. Then please head over when the time comes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Time passes quickly. Before you know it, it is two in the afternoon..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
