    "801204": {
        "Desc": "Return to Eide's house",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Curses... Forest Rangers."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Forest Ranger",
                    "T": "Hey! Who are you? We haven't seen you around here before. What's your business here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Have you seen a hilichurl? A hilichurl should have come past this way... have you seen it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Forest Ranger",
                    "T": "I asked you first... Don't make this more difficult than it needs to be!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I said... have you seen... a HILICHURL!!!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Eide..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Forest Ranger",
                    "T": "Hey, whoa... Look, Sir, there's no need to get so worked up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Forest Ranger",
                    "T": "There are hilichurls everywhere, what's the big deal? We see plenty of them out here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ranger Guard",
                    "T": "Exactly. Matter of fact, we just took out a few of them back there. Those dumb boneheads..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "You... you...!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Forest Ranger scum! You spawn of The Seven are all the same! I'll have your heads if you so much as laid a finger on Caribert!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Forest Ranger",
                    "T": "You...! You're raving mad! You've got some gall, coming here to our nation, insulting the Forest Rangers!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Curse you all, Forest Rangers..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Stop it, Eide!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Stop. Or the Forest Rangers and I will have to make you."
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "Both sides calm down for now, thanks to your urging..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ranger Guard",
                    "T": "I don't get it. Why make such a huge fuss over a few hilichurls...? It makes no sense..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "You..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "He'd only just regained his mind. How could you do this to him..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "So tell me, Forest Rangers... Did you really spare none of them? Did you really take out every last hilichurl you saw?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ranger Guard",
                    "T": "Geez, you're really not gonna let this go... Fine, you weirdo. If you must know, I happened to cross paths with a solitary hilichurl when I left the team to, uh... use the toilet."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ranger Guard",
                    "T": "I was frightened at first, but it didn't seem to have any interest in me at all. It was just bumbling along, in... that direction. So I left it alone."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "There's still hope!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Yes! Wonderful... Wonderful. Let's go! We have to find him!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Forest Ranger",
                    "T": "Wait, you're leaving? Not even a \"Thanks for the info, goodbye\"?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
