    "801207": {
        "Desc": "Talk to the Forest Rangers",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...Haha, I see, I understand now..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Finally, it all makes sense..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(What happened... did I faint? I remember Caribert taking his mask off, but then...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Aha, Traveler, you're awake... Finally, we can rejoice together!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Wait, no... Why am I still calling you \"Traveler\"? I have known your true identity for some time now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What do you mean, \"true identity\"?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Eide, are you okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Hehehe... I suspected it was you from the beginning! I had to talk to you to be sure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But I've never met you..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Oh, of course you haven't. With your status? You can hardly be expected to know all of us."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "In any case... I've been using a fake name this entire time. \"Eide\" is the name of a servant I once had..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "My real name is Chlothar..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...Chlothar Alberich."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Alberich!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You can't be!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "You saw it too, didn't you? Unmistakable... The power inside Caribert and the power of the one you call a \"Sinner,\" it was one and the same..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I am positive now... it's the power of the Abyss, isn't it?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "At long last, I have seen it with my own eyes..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I didn't see clearly..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What happened to Caribert?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "That is no business of yours!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "A sinner... Yes, salvation for a sinner can only come from a sinner..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Caribert did not deserve his fate, but now... It's wonderful â€” he will be able to weave his own destiny anew."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "Born into abject sorrow, he shall now become..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...\"The Loom of Fate.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(There's that term again... the \"Loom of Fate\"...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You're right about this being from the Abyss..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But the Abyss is sinister and dangerous..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...Sinister? ...Dangerous?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "I never imagined that you, of all people, would deny the Abyss... How ridiculous!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "We once believed that you would bring new strength and hope to Khaenri'ah."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "To us, you were the Abyss... A wondrous mystery far beyond our imagination and comprehension..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "...And the one who controls the Abyss can control everything!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "We yearned for that future. We looked to you to take us there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "But what did you bring us instead?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eide",
                    "T": "#O {M#Princess}{F#Prince}... of Khaenri'ah?"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
